title: Vestal girls continue to roll in win over M-E
text: Friday, October 09, 2015 - 4:32:43 AM Local Sports Vestal girls continue to roll in win over M-E 10/8/2015 (Updated 10:50:46 PM) The Vestal Golden Bears are the third ranked team in the state in Class A and continue their impressive roll. They beat the host Maine-Endwell Spartans Thursday 3-0 with all goals coming in the second half. Vestal is now 11-0 and still has yet to allow a goal on the season.
